sequenceDiagram
    participant T1 as order-worker-1
    participant T2 as order-worker-2
    participant L as orderLock
    participant S as stockLock

    T1->>L: 拿到 orderLock
    T2->>L: 等待 orderLock
    T1->>S: 拿到 stockLock
    T1->>T1: 执行完成
    T1->>S: 释放 stockLock
    T1->>L: 释放 orderLock
    T2->>L: 拿到 orderLock
    T2->>T2: 继续执行